body:
Unable to create **Euclid Flex Thin** font. I have used below code.
`SKTypeface typeFace = SKTypeface.FromFamilyName(@"Euclid Flex", SKFontStyleWeight.Thin, SKFontStyleWidth.Normal, SKFontStyleSlant.Upright);`

If we save the stream as a file, it shows the font name **Euclid Flex Ultralight**.

```
FileStream fontStream = new FileStream(@"D:\EuclidFont.otf", FileMode.Create, FileAccess.Write);  
  SKStreamAsset stream = typeFace.OpenStream();
            if (stream != null && stream.Length > 0)
            {
                byte[] fontData = new byte[stream.Length - 1];
                stream.Read(fontData, stream.Length);
                stream.Dispose();
                MemoryStream m_stream = new MemoryStream(fontData);
                m_stream.CopyTo(fontStream);
                fontStream.Flush();
            }
```

SkiaSharp version - 1.59.3
NET Core 2.0
